items.title: Awesome Cl
items.content_text:
### Graph databases

*   [neo4cl](https://codeberg.org/Equill/neo4cl) - a library for interacting with Neo4J. Sends Cypher queries to a Neo4J server, and decodes the responses into something useful for processing in CL. [Apache2](https://directory.fsf.org/wiki/License:Apache2.0).
    *   and maybe: [cl-neo4j (‚≠ê26)](https://github.com/kraison/cl-neo4j) - a thin neo4j RESTFUL client interface.

items.title: Urban and Regional Planning Resources
items.content_text:
### Platforms and Software Resources / Environmental and Climate Planning Tools and Platforms

*   [Temperate](https://icleiusa.org/temperate-adaptation-planner/) - This user-friendly tool was developed by Azavea in partnership with ICLEI USA, with the primary purpose of facilitating a data-informed adaptation planning process in small-to-midsize communities with little to no devoted resources to plan for climate change impacts.
